</paragraph>
<paragraph id="142F35B341AC3A46A2F6235CAD0F410D" pageId="186" pageNumber="187">
EGYPT, Sinai, Wadi Feiran, 
<emphasis id="CEA726607C0607983BD23C3D746000D4" italics="true" pageId="186" pageNumber="187">March</emphasis>
s.n. (lectotype GOET, designated by 
<bibRefCitation id="3988F31316FA2125EB130DA1EFD40451" author="Sa'ad, F" journalOrPublisher="Bronder Offset, Rotterdam" pageId="210" pageNumber="211" pagination="1 - 287" refId="B314" refString="Sa'ad, F, 1967. The Convolvulus species of the Canary Isles, the Mediterranean region, and the Near and Middle East. Mededelingen van het Botanisch Museum en Herbarium van de Rijksuniversite Utrecht. Bronder Offset, Rotterdam: 1 - 287" title="The Convolvulus species of the Canary Isles, the Mediterranean region, and the Near and Middle East. Mededelingen van het Botanisch Museum en Herbarium van de Rijksuniversite Utrecht" year="1967">
